==English==

===Noun===
'''frigidity'''

# The state of being [[frigid]]; [[coldness]]; lack of [[heat]]. 
# Coldness of feeling, manner or quality; lack of [[ardor]], [[animation]] or [[vivacity]]; [[chilliness]]; [[dullness]].
# Want of [[natural]] [[heat]] and [[vigor]] of body; [[impotency]].

